{"about_the_game":"<strong>Introducing Single-Player Mode to Akpala, the VR Magic Battle Game with Voice Recognition!</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166600/extras/Create-Your-Own-Story.png?t=1729626612\" /><br><br>&quot;Tarnished Wings&quot; is the first DLC for Akpala, bringing the much-expected single-player mode to the game!<br><br>In this scenario, you'll embark on an adventure as Castiel, a celestial guardian. While on a mission to protect someone dear to you, you suddenly face an incredibly difficult choice...<br><br>Enjoy the story while exploring new locations and battling powerful bosses. It's an action RPG you can play solo!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166600/extras/Your-Choices-Shape-the-World!.png?t=1729626612\" /><br><br>Will this game end happily? Or will it be a tragic conclusion? The truth is, no one knows yet.<br><br>The story changes based on your choices and how you fight. While the original tutorial allowed you to converse with AI characters, this new single-player mode introduces AI characters as enemies as well.<br><br>Can you outsmart these AI adversaries?<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166600/extras/New-Item-System.png?t=1729626612\" /><br><br>In single-player mode, you can acquire potions and weapons. Use your limited resources wisely to overcome challenges and unravel mysteries!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3166600/extras/Game-System.png?t=1729626612\" /><br><br>By purchasing this downloadable content, you'll gain full access to the single-player mode &quot;Tarnished Wings&quot;.","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3166600?t=1729626612","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/s